WEBVTT

1
00:18:52.910 --> 00:18:54.170 
她们回来了
There they are.

2
00:18:54.170 --> 00:18:56.670 
你们俩早上有按时把车还回去吗
Did you girls get the car back in time this morning?

3
00:18:56.670 --> 00:18:59.010 
有  时间刚刚好  多亏了卡洛琳
Yep, just in time, thanks to Caroline.

4
00:18:59.010 --> 00:19:00.750 
她完全无视限速的标志
She was ignoring speed limit signs

5
00:19:00.750 --> 00:19:03.260 
就像她无视流浪汉一样
like she does homeless people.

6
00:19:04.120 --> 00:19:06.020 
有个州警用四个字形容我开车
A state trooper called my driving

7
00:19:06.020 --> 00:19:08.110 
"刑事过失"
criminally negligent.

8
00:19:08.600 --> 00:19:10.500 
我真为你骄傲
I was so proud.

9
00:19:10.500 --> 00:19:11.770 
当时差点都要感动落泪了
I might've even gotten emotional,

10
00:19:11.770 --> 00:19:13.300 
但我必须巧舌如簧求警察别开罚单
but I had to talk our way out of the ticket,

11
00:19:13.300 --> 00:19:17.170 
还得在脱衣色诱时保持专业  所以没哭
and I like to be professional when my shirt's off.

12
00:19:17.470 --> 00:19:19.080 
你们没被开罚单吗
You didn't get a ticket?

13
00:19:19.080 --> 00:19:23.570 
昨天我就因为走进全食超市而被捕了
Yesterday, I got arrested for just walking into Whole Foods.

